const ScrollDrawing = () => {
  const [initial, setInitial] = useState(false);
  const [showLinesSecond, setShowLinesSecond] = useState(false);
  const [showLinesThird, setShowLinesThird] = useState(false);
  const [showLinesFourth, setShowLinesFourth] = useState(false);
  const [showLinesFifth, setShowLinesFifth] = useState(false);
  const [showLinesSixth, setShowLinesSixth] = useState(false);
  const [showLinesSeventh, setShowLinesSeventh] = useState(false);
  const [step, setStep] = useState(0);
  const [currentStep, setCurrentStep] = useState(0);

  const steps = [
    "initial",
    "showLinesSecond",
    "showLinesThird",
    "showLinesFourth",
    "showLinesFifth",
    "showLinesSixth",
    "showLinesSeventh",
  ];
  const toggleLines = () => {
    // Toggle the current state
    if (currentStep < steps.length) {
      const currentState = steps[currentStep];
      switch (currentState) {
        case "initial":
          setInitial(!initial);
          break;
        case "showLinesSecond":
          setShowLinesSecond(!showLinesSecond);
          break;
        case "showLinesThird":
          setShowLinesThird(!showLinesThird);
          break;
        case "showLinesFourth":
          setShowLinesFourth(!showLinesFourth);
          break;
        case "showLinesFifth":
          setShowLinesFifth(!showLinesFifth);
          break;
        case "showLinesSixth":
          setShowLinesSixth(!showLinesSixth);
          break;
        case "showLinesSeventh":
          setShowLinesSeventh(!showLinesSeventh);
          break;
        default:
          break;
      }

      setCurrentStep(currentStep + 1);
    }
  };

  const [linesDelay, setLinesDelay] = useState(0);
  useEffect(() => {
    if (showLinesFifth) {
      const lineElements = document.querySelectorAll(".animated-line");
      lineElements.forEach((line, index) => {
        // Delay each line's appearance by 100ms
        setTimeout(() => {
          // Apply the transformation to move from right to the actual position
          line.style.transform = "translateX(0)";
          line.style.transition = "transform 1s ease";
        }, linesDelay + 100 * index);
      });
    } else {
      // Reset line transformations when hiding
      const lineElements = document.querySelectorAll(".animated-line");
      lineElements.forEach((line) => {
        // Apply the transformation to move from the actual position to the left
        line.style.transform = "translateX(-100%)";
        line.style.transition = "transform 0.5s ease";
      });
    }
  }, [showLinesFifth, linesDelay]);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (initial) {
      const rectElements = document.querySelectorAll(".animated-rect");
      rectElements.forEach((rect, index) => {
        // Delay each rect's appearance by 500ms (adjust this value as needed)
        setTimeout(() => {
          rect.style.opacity = 1;
        }, linesDelay + 500 * index);
      });
    }
  }, [initial, linesDelay]);

  return (
    <div className="bg-black py-20">
      <button className="bg-white p-4 ml-10" onClick={toggleLines}>
        {currentStep < steps.length
          ? `Toggle ${
              steps[currentStep].charAt(0).toUpperCase() +
              steps[currentStep].slice(1)
            } Scroll`
          : "All Steps Toggled"}
      </button>
